<br>
Doing splits near the spawn points.<br>
Agro 2 mobs, go a little bit away, FD.<br>
When 1 of them goes back to their spawn point (let as much time pass by as possible before the 2nd starts walking away), stand up, run a little farther and FD.  The one that stayed the first time will immediately walk away while the other stays.  Stand up and bring the one that stayed completely alone.<br>
I know this looks like bringing the mob on the first FD would be easier.  But there are places where this tactic works best.<br>
(I practiced this in IWK, came in handy for otherwise linked mobs)<br>
<br>
Blurring<br>
